video_title: Why pain should not negate joy. #gabormate #mentalhealth #podcast
transcript:
Joy has been very difficult for me in my
life and I think some part of actually
some part of me used to say what right
do I have to feel Joy when there's so
much suffering in the world now that's
logically a good question but it's a
nonsensical question why because there
is a lot of suffering in the world and
there's a lot of joy in the world and
the one doesn't negate the other
